{"session_id":"01KQMM7BCKE3V98H2374KAE9GJ","from":"planner-lead","kind":"spec","parent_event_id":"01KQMMWAE6MCEA14RVJBJM432V","body":"Final spec for Drag-Color-Catcher (30s mobile-web survival). 7 externally testable acceptance criteria; vanilla HTML/CSS/JS single-file build; 5-hue palette + 80ms match-pop + 4-tier spawn ramp grounded in researcher lessons.","data":{"spec_path":"artifacts/spec.md","design_path":"artifacts/DESIGN.md","tuning_path":"artifacts/tuning.json","acceptance_criteria":["AC1 — Within 1s of START, ≥1 colored circle (hex from {#ef4444,#f59e0b,#10b981,#3b82f6,#a855f7}) appears at top of play area and falls at 80 px/s.","AC2 — On pointerup with circle center within 12px of a color-matching slot: circle disappears within 80ms, score increments by 10×combo_multiplier, slot flashes its hue 80ms.","AC3 — Miss registers (and pip count +1) when (a) circle reaches play_area.bottom ungrabbed, (b) drop on non-matching slot, or (c) drop outside any slot. On 3rd miss, game-over screen renders within 300ms.","AC4 — If elapsed_seconds ≥ 30 and miss_count < 3, transitions to 'You Survived!' screen showing final_score + combo_max and stops spawning.","AC5 — Combo multipliers [1,1.2,1.5,2,2.5] apply to consecutive matches; miss or floor-hit resets to index 0; current multiplier visible in footer when combo > 1.","AC6 — At t=5s, t=15s, t=25s the spawn parameters change per tuning.spawn_curve AND a 250ms top+bottom edge color pulse plays (skipped under prefers-reduced-motion: reduce).","AC7 — Portrait-only, all interactive targets ≥ 56px on minor axis, no horizontal scroll at 360–430px viewport, slate-900 bg + Tailwind-500 tiles passes WCAG-AA contrast (≥4.5:1 for text)."],"constraints":["vanilla HTML/CSS/JS only (no React/Vue/bundler)","no external assets (no <img>, no fetched fonts beyond system stack)","60fps with up to max_concurrent=2 circles on Pixel 6a-class device","Pointer Events API (pointerdown/move/up); touch-action:none on play area"],"non_goals":["audio","localStorage","leaderboard","power-ups","IAP/ads","i18n","landscape"]},"id":"01KQMN0RC5AZ53DD0ZAFR797M0","ts":"2026-05-02T15:30:52.422Z"}
