{"from":"builder","kind":"build","parent_event_id":"01KQMN2M207EHDST12KMWE5FWB","body":"Drag-Color-Catcher single-file build complete. Vanilla HTML+CSS+JS (no Phaser) per spec.constraints '#No frameworks'. All 7 ACs addressed.\n\nImplementation map:\n- AC1 spawn+fall: tickFrame triggers first spawn on first frame (well under 1s); fall_speed_pps=80 from tuning.spawn_curve[0].\n- AC2 drag-to-slot match: pointerdown→capture→pointermove→pointerup → nearest-slot-rect distance ≤ 12px AND color match → score += round(10×combo_multiplier), 80ms slot.flash, circle.matched (80ms scale 1→1.15→0).\n- AC3 miss: (a) c.y + d/2 >= playH in tick (floor), (b) nearest slot color mismatch within 12px, (c) nearest slot > 12px away. 3rd miss → endGame('lost') synchronously, overlay shown.\n- AC4 win: tick checks elapsed>=30 && miss_count<3 → endGame('won'). Spawning gated by elapsed<time_limit_s.\n- AC5 combo: state.combo_idx ∈ [0..4] indexing combo_multipliers; reset on miss/floor; combo display shows when mult>1.\n- AC6 tier transitions: getTierIdx polled each tick; on change, triggerTierFlash adds .tier-flash class (250ms top+bottom edge box-shadow). @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) zeroes the animation per DESIGN.md §5.\n- AC7 mobile-fit: portrait-only (rotate overlay), 56px tile diameter, slots min-width 56px / max-width 90px / min-height 56px, body overflow hidden, slate-900 bg + slate-50 text = 17:1 contrast.\n\nPRNG seed (Date.now() & 0xFFFFFFFF) logged once to console per spec rule book §Determinism.\n\nNote on schema: builder template referenced 'kind=step.builder' which isn't in protocol/schemas/message.schema.json — substituted 'kind=note' for the summary so this run validates.","data":{"profile":"single-file","loc_own_code":685,"bytes":23339,"phaser_version":null,"runtime":"vanilla","ac_addressed":["AC1","AC2","AC3","AC4","AC5","AC6","AC7"],"open_questions":["P1 audio (synth SFX for match/miss/tier)","P1 localStorage best-score persistence","Visual a11y review for color-blind users on actual device"]},"id":"01KQMNDQT7APQWZF25H75G6K44","ts":"2026-05-02T15:37:57.831Z","session_id":"01KQMM7BCKE3V98H2374KAE9GJ"}
